{"tid":2096622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保就業計劃過百間公司承諾受薪人數為零　個別獲逾十萬元補貼","createTime":"2020-07-06T08:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T09:11:54.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d19728055b0538eb3c66ae4333921d09520b67","tid":2096622,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府公布第三批保就業計劃的僱主名單，當中過百名僱主報稱承諾受薪人數為零，但同樣獲得補貼，個別更獲得超過十萬元補貼。本台向創新辦查詢，暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n保就業計劃第三批名單，涉及約三萬名僱主，總補貼額約77億元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中原地產</span>成為取得最多補貼的僱主，綜合之前公布兩輪僱主名單，首次有公司獲得過億元補貼，涉及1.15億元，公司承諾補貼期內維持約5600名員工。<br />\n<br />\n多間以零售為主的公司都榜上有名，<span style=\"color: red;\">周大福</span>獲得約7700萬補貼、<span style=\"color: red;\">莎莎</span>有近6000萬元，補貼額在已公布僱主名單中分別排第四及五跟之前公布的名單不同，這次出現大量「零僱員」的公司。<br />\n<br />\n在保就業計劃下，申請的僱主要承諾在補貼期內不裁員，維持申請時的僱員人數，但有<span style=\"color: red;\">140間公司承諾受薪僱員人數是零</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=396937&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396937%26home%3D1&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=8e1a4d14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396937%26home%3D1&h=d011f955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=396937&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"8f96f656e1d2b65f77a6858263612200107ee722","tid":2096622,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe8d2241ebd8f1f22a83f581fe5961e39f673f4","tid":2096622,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"個老細自己請返自己<br />\n一個月幾皮<br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36276b3198af1c994ff2240c4cd6cb55037efa3","tid":2096622,"uid":56115,"like":0,"di